<plot>On the planet Venus, it rains almost constantly. A classroom full of young children are excited to hear that the rain will stop today, for just fifteen minutes. But they are also resentful of a new classmate from Earth, who remembers what it's like to see the sun. They lock her in a closet just before the sun comes out.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?030984</url></doc>
